However, the focus on maximizing the probability of the observed profile rather than the observed values suggests that the paper is more likely to belong to sub-categories that deal with information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), data mining (cs.DM), and computational complexity (cs.CC).
